    {
        "content": "<p>I know this is not technically the same (leans reals are infinite precision) but just in case someone doubts these:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Math</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sqrt</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Math</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">floor</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Math</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sqrt</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n<span class=\"mf\">0.41421356237309515</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Math</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sqrt</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Math</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">floor</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Math</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sqrt</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">10</span>\n<span class=\"mf\">0.014213562373095234</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
